BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-24T22:00:00&endDate=2026-06-25T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Wednesday 24 June\, from 2300\, no eastbound service from Willesden Junction to Stratford after 2300. Customers should use the last eastbound services detailed below or London Overground services to Euston. Last through trains: Clapham Junction to Stratford 2218\; Richmond to Stratford 2232\; Willesden Junction to Stratford 2252. The 2249 train from Richmond to Stratford will not run\, the 2302 train from Richmond to Stratford will terminate at Willesden Junction and the 2318 train from Richmond to Willesden Junction will not run
DTEND:20260625T002900Z
DTSTART:20260624T220000Z
SUMMARY:Mildmay line: Part Closure
UID:e2b28e9f-8fa7-455b-8b10-f5f97fb72529@e2b2.org
END:VEVENT
